rows.label: qst202716_msg0001
rows.name: ...M-meh? What happen to ritual?

rows.label: qst202716_msg0002
rows.name: It got canceled.

rows.label: qst202716_msg0003
rows.name:
It's no big loss. You could never hope
to change the world that way, anyway.

rows.label: qst202716_msg0004
rows.name:
All you were doing is
throwing your lives away.

rows.label: qst202716_msg0005
rows.name: You...

rows.label: qst202716_msg0006
rows.name:
Came here to find you,
on your mother's orders.

rows.label: qst202716_msg0007
rows.name:
You made your mom sick with worry.
And you caused no end of hassle
to me and mine...

rows.label: qst202716_msg0008
rows.name: I hope you're sorry.

rows.label: qst202716_msg0009
rows.name:
We...are Nopon. With strength
of Nopon, we can save Alst...

rows.label: qst202716_msg0010
rows.name:
That is what we believed. They said
we can change the world, and we
believed we can do anything.

rows.label: qst202716_msg0011
rows.name:
But...it was mistake, in the end...
We sorry.

rows.label: qst202716_msg0012
rows.name: Hey, I don't wanna hear it.

rows.label: qst202716_msg0013
rows.name:
You should be apologizing to your
mother, not to me. She's the one
who's been worrying non-stop.

rows.label: qst202716_msg0014
rows.name: My...mamapon?

rows.label: qst202716_msg0015
rows.name:
You get it now?
I'm not saying you can't rebel.

rows.label: qst202716_msg0016
rows.name:
But if you're gonna, you have to be
aware of the consequences and ready
to take responsibility.

rows.label: qst202716_msg0017
rows.name:
Otherwise, you're nothing but
a snotty kid acting out.

rows.label: qst202716_msg0018
rows.name: All right?

rows.label: qst202716_msg0019
rows.name: All right...

rows.label: qst202716_msg0020
rows.name:
Well, if it's all right, then hurry up and
let's mosey on home. We'll make sure
you get there OK.
